                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='22375' id='203' type-v2='text' w='30900' x='35700' y='22750'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe WPC,Segoe UI,sans-serif' fontsize='7'>Trawlers</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe WPC,Segoe UI,sans-serif' fontsize='7'> Highest benthic and bycatch impact; most destructive gear type globally</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe WPC,Segoe UI,sans-serif' fontsize='7'>Drifting Longlines</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe WPC,Segoe UI,sans-serif' fontsize='7'> Bycatch-dominant method; major threat to sharks, seabirds, and turtles</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe WPC,Segoe UI,sans-serif' fontsize='7'>Purse Seines </run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe WPC,Segoe UI,sans-serif' fontsize='7'>Strong pelagic impact; encircles entire schools of open-water fish</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe WPC,Segoe UI,sans-serif' fontsize='7'>Pots and Traps </run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe WPC,Segoe UI,sans-serif' fontsize='7'>Passive, trap-based method; moderate impact with low habitat damage</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe WPC,Segoe UI,sans-serif' fontsize='7'>Pole and Line </run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe WPC,Segoe UI,sans-serif' fontsize='7'>Most sustainable method; minimal bycatch and near-zero habitat impact</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                  </zone-style>
